<br>
Take the world, make it what you want. Or take history as it is and rewrite it. Bah, what's the difference? Sure... Others may point and laugh (at least, hopefully in regards to Rutabagas) but never, ever, EVER let anyone, such as haters, RPG players, GM events (ones where they don't kill your character at least), Verant, storylines, etc. etc. etc. get in the way of your roleplaying! Also, timing is everything! Sometimes, people laugh at the punchline, sometimes they don't. Sometimes the GMs will summon plagues for you, sometimes they won't. Sometimes you feel like a nut... sometimes you... -- err, where was I?<br>
<br>
Oh yes, how I do ramble... *ahem*<br>
<br>
I hereby salute Banegrivm! True, we may look at EverQuest differently, but there are at least a couple of ways we are similar, Banegrivm and I. ... and many, many, many ways we are different.  For instance, our choice in Kool-Aid flavors.  I am a large fan of Grape, but Banegrivm is no doubt, a Cherry sort of guy.  YET, he doesn't scoff at us for not tossing out ye's and haths, and hath nots...  - rather we toss out &quot;Wheees&quot; and &quot;NYYYEEEERs&quot;  and &quot;Whooops&quot; and &quot;nyuks&quot; and I don't scoff at him for his inability to spray milk out of his nose.  This is a good thing too!  For if he did, most certainly, it would douse out his enchanted flaming sword; making that ruby-red rubicite turn an odd shade of... perywinkle. .. and where would the world of Norrath be? Well, let me tell you roleplaya' hata's exactly where it would be! It would be exactly as my demented twisted plan of world domination had designed it to be, but that's not the point my darling lambchops! - Err.. what was my point? .. Hmm. I dunno, but...  Uhhh...   I hereby raise my glass of milk in honor of Banegrivm, for all the drama , the joy, and laughter and tears, and those late nights in Mistmoore hearing &quot;Incommeth!&quot; followed by &quot;You have been slain by a Thought Defiler!&quot; followed by, &quot;LOADING, PLEASE WAIT...&quot;, and - did I mention laughter? - everything else that he has brought us year after year, and server, after server....<br>
<br>
<br>
/bows humbly <br>
<br>
Hail Banegrivm, whatever server and/or RPG he is in.  <p> 

